      | destination | "Hà Giang" |
      | company     | "Cau Me"   |
      | leaveAt     | "10:30"    |
    Then The document "bus-4-vn" content match:
      | destination | "Sa Pa"   |
      | company     | "So Viet" |
      | leaveAt     | "10:30"   |
